---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';

import HeroImage from '../assets/images/image-web-3-mobile.jpg';
import FigmaImage from '../assets/images/heroheader.png?url';

import { Image } from '@astrojs/image/components';
---

<Layout title="News Homepage">
  <main>
    <Header />
    <div>
      <!-- <Image
        height={300}
        class="hero-image-mobile"
        src={FigmaImage}
        alt="Test"
      /> -->
      <img class="hero-image-mobile" src={FigmaImage} />
      <!-- <img class="hero-image-mobile" src={HeroImage} alt="" /> -->
    </div>
    <h1>The Bright Future of Web 3.0?</h1>

    <p>
      We dive into the next evolution of the web that claims to put the power of
      the platforms back into the hands of the people. But is it really
      fulfilling its promise?
    </p>

    <a href="/future-of-web-3">Read more</a>

    <h2>New</h2>

    <h3>Hydrogen VS Electric Cars</h3>
    <p>Will hydrogen-fueled cars ever catch up to EVs?</p>

    <h3>The Downsides of AI Artistry</h3>
    <p>
      What are the possible adverse effects of on-demand AI image generation?
    </p>
    <h3>Is VC Funding Drying Up?</h3>
    <p>
      Private funding by VC firms is down 50% YOY. We take a look at what that
      means.
    </p>

    <span>01</span>
    <h4>Reviving Retro PCs</h4>
    <p>happens when old PCs are given modern upgrades?</p>

    <span>02</span>
    <h4>Top 10 Laptops of 2022</h4>
    <p>Our best picks for various needs and budgets.</p>

    <span>03</span>
    <h4>The Growth of Gaming</h4>
    <p>How the pandemic has sparked fresh opportunities.</p>

    <div class="attribution">
      Challenge by <a
        href="https://www.frontendmentor.io?ref=challenge"
        target="_blank">Frontend Mentor</a
      >. Coded by <a href="#">Your Name Here</a>.
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    padding: 28px 16px;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--almostWhite);
  }

  .hero-image-mobile {
    width: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .attribution {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .attribution a {
    color: hsl(228, 45%, 44%);
  }
</style>
